 Velmor Delicacies - Restaurant Menu

This project is a simple, static HTML and CSS website for the Velmor Delicacies restaurant menu. It displays the restaurant's logo, a structured menu with appetizers, main courses, and desserts, and a link to a contact page.



Clean Menu Layout:** The menu is broken down into three main sections:
    Appetizers
    Main Courses
    Desserts
Visuals:** Each menu item includes a name, price, description, and a representative image.
Contact Link:** A clear link at the bottom directs users to the contact page for reservations or catering.

 Tech 

HTML5:Used for the structure and content of the website.
CSS3: (via `global.css`) Used for styling, layout, and visual appearance.

